# ─── Build Output ───────────────────────────────────────────────
build/
out/
cmake-build-*/
*.elf
*.bin
*.hex
*.map
*.lst
*.axf

# ─── CMake Generated ────────────────────────────────────────────
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
